trans-unit.source: Compares two objects for equivalence, ignoring the case of strings.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligner to objekter for likhet, ignorerer bokstavtypen for strenger.

trans-unit.source: CaseInsensitiveComparer implements the <xref:System.Collections.IComparer> interface supporting case-insensitive comparisons on strings, just as <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider> implements the <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider> interface supporting case-insensitive comparisons on strings.
trans-unit.target: CaseInsensitiveComparer implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IComparer>grensesnittet støtter sammenligning av strenger, like <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider>implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider>grensesnittet støtter sammenligninger i strenger.</xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider> </xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider> </xref:System.Collections.IComparer>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Comparer> class is the default implementation of the <xref:System.Collections.IComparer> interface and performs case-sensitive string comparisons.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Collections.Comparer>klassen er standard implementering av den <xref:System.Collections.IComparer>grensesnittet og utfører skiller strengsammenligninger.</xref:System.Collections.IComparer> </xref:System.Collections.Comparer>

trans-unit.source: The objects used as keys by a <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> are required to override the <xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method (or the <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider> interface) and the <xref:System.Object.Equals%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method (or the <xref:System.Collections.IComparer> interface).
trans-unit.target: Objekter som brukes som nøkler av en <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>kreves for å overstyre den <xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden (eller <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider>grensesnittet) og <xref:System.Object.Equals%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden (eller <xref:System.Collections.IComparer>grensesnittet).</xref:System.Collections.IComparer> </xref:System.Object.Equals%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider> </xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>

trans-unit.source: The implementation of both methods or interfaces must handle case sensitivity the same way; otherwise, the <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> might behave incorrectly.
trans-unit.target: Implementeringen av både metoder eller grensesnitt må behandle store og små bokstaver på samme måte; Hvis ikke, den <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>fungerer på feil måte.</xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>

trans-unit.source: For example, when creating a <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>, you must use this class with the <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider> class or any case-insensitive <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider> implementation.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel når du oppretter en <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>, må du bruke denne klassen med den <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider>klasse eller en samlingstype <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider>implementering.</xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider> </xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider> </xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>

trans-unit.source: String comparisons might have different results depending on the culture.
trans-unit.target: Strengsammenligninger kan ha forskjellige resultater, alt etter kulturen.

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> for gjeldende tråd.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer> instance is created using this constructor, the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> of the current thread is saved.

trans-unit.source: Performs a case-insensitive comparison of two objects of the same type and returns a value indicating whether one is less than, equal to, or greater than the other.
trans-unit.target: Utfører en samlingstype sammenligning av to objekter av samme type, og returnerer en verdi som angir om en er mindre enn, lik eller større enn den andre.

trans-unit.source: If `a` and `b` are both strings, this method uses <xref:System.Globalization.CompareInfo.Compare%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to compare the strings with the casing ignored; otherwise, it uses the <xref:System.IComparable> implementation of either object.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `a` og `b` er begge strenger, denne metoden bruker <xref:System.Globalization.CompareInfo.Compare%2A?displayProperty=fullName>strenger med kabinettet sammenlignes ignorert; ellers den bruker den <xref:System.IComparable>implementeringen av objekt.</xref:System.IComparable> </xref:System.Globalization.CompareInfo.Compare%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: That is, if `a` implements <xref:System.IComparable>, then this method returns the result of `a`.
trans-unit.target: Det vil si hvis `a` implementerer <xref:System.IComparable>, og denne metoden returnerer resultatet av `a`.</xref:System.IComparable>

trans-unit.source: `CompareTo` (`b`); otherwise, if `b` implements <xref:System.IComparable>, then it returns the negated result of `b`.
trans-unit.target: `CompareTo`(`b`); Ellers hvis `b` implementerer <xref:System.IComparable>, og returnerer den negative resultatet av `b`.</xref:System.IComparable>

trans-unit.source: `CompareTo` (`a`).
trans-unit.target: `CompareTo` (`a`).

trans-unit.source: Comparing `null` with any type is allowed and does not generate an exception when using <xref:System.IComparable>.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligning av `null` med et hvilket som er tillatt, og ikke generere et unntak ved <xref:System.IComparable>.</xref:System.IComparable>

trans-unit.source: When sorting, `null` is considered to be less than any other object.
trans-unit.target: Når du sorterer, `null` anses å være mindre enn andre objekter.
